  "instructions": [
    "Cook the rice noodles according to package instructions and set aside.",
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the Thai chilies and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cooked noodles, soy sauce, and lime juice to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly, until the noodles are well coated.",
    "Transfer the noodles to a serving platter and top with toasted peanuts and scallions.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
